'''Erik Tiemens''' made the original art used to sculpt the [[Great Hyperspace War Bas-Relief|Massassi frieze]] for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. He also wrote and drew the comic ''[[The Artist of Naboo]]'' for ''[[Star Wars: Visionaries]]'' and did concept art for [[Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens|''Star Wars'': Episode VII ''The Force Awakens'']].{{Mediacat|imagecat=images by Erik Tiemens}}

